Comment: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:07.52,Title,,0,0,0,,Zenny of the Island of Goats and \Nthe Pirate Ship In the Mountains!
Comment: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:35.51,Title,,0,0,0,,How's Tricks? \NThe Designs of Zenny the Moneylender!
Comment: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,NOTES
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,OPENING
Comment: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ENDING
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After them! Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I thought they were these great pirates,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but these fainthearted guys are \Njust running away, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.72,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant, let's be the ones who \Nbring in the Straw Hat pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring them in, for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.81,0:02:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! \NIf we don't do something, they really will hit us!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too hungry...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.06,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, these Navy guys are pesky.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you caught anything yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of catching something!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a single drop of water left!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.24,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're either going \Nto shrivel up, or die of starvation.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}, it's time for afternoon tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.62,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you care for some mille-feuille, as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mister cook.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a snack, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, where the hell did you have that hidden?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys keep your mitts off of this!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the lack of a sense of urgency?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this any time to be laughing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, this sea looks even \Nmore alarming than the Navy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your navigating skills and do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,More fog?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.37,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We might be able to use this \Nfog to give the Navy the slip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.66,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this water is moving fast. \NWhat's more, there are reefs everywhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This region of the ocean is designated \Nas a class-one danger zone!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursuing them any farther is impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, we'll be wiped out!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! We've chased them this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We've almost got them, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sergeant, let's finish this now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw. Come about at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got orders from Captain Moore
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.54,0:04:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that once we spot the Straw Hat pirates, \Nwe are to eliminate them!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pestering me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.17,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain is not in command right now. \NI am. Understood?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.09,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard aport! Pull the sail 45° to the left!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of the fog.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, an island! I see an island!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it has something to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Six people and one animal...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter how many \Nof you damn pirates there are.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you watch this...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's uninhabited.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.17,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,– A goat? \N– M-Meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.80,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat! Meat! Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I don't care how hungry you are,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't just go after that cute little goat!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the cute little goats \Nhave taken a liking to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.75,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trap! We've fallen into their trap!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cut them, Zoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys aren't bad! I can tell that much!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabasco Star!!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The goat kicked it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.65,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! We're not going to eat you or anything! \NI promise!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you all set a trap for us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? They were ordered by somebody to do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody who?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Keep out of the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.84,0:07:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A weird old man fell out of there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.15,0:07:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper, is this the man who \Ngave the goats their orders?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They say yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.20,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have thought we \Nwere here to attack him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. \NWe just want some water and provisions.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I trust anything a pirate says?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you right now, there's no \Ntreasure on this island, got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am penniless!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look very rich, in any case.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.76,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn pirates! \NIf that's how you want it, I'll be a man about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Simmer me, bake me, do whatever you will!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.02,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? I'm a cook. \NSimmering and baking are my specialty.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.44,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait! I was just joking! \NYou fiend! You scoundrel! You killer!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone limp.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The old man's grit is amazing, \Nbut he's pretty fainthearted.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! His heart has stopped!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,– Zoro! \N– You ogre!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,– How cruel! \N– Mossy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold on, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor! \NLet's hurry and take the old man to his house!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.94,0:09:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very nearly killed out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't drop your guard around a pirate.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to you! You fainted all on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Old goat man, did your heart stop out of shock?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here in the Grand Line, \Nthere must be surprises every day.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you've lasted this long, \Nwith that faint heart of yours.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, we're glad that you're life isn't in danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there to be glad about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.84,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already scared the hell out of me, \Nand nearly got me killed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, now I can't chop firewood, \Nor draw any water.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out a whole bunch, here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.48,0:09:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Altogether, I've lost 50,000,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.69,0:09:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overcharging, aren't you? \NAt the most, it should be this much.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're being stingy! \NEven with a huge discount, it's this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you subtract Chopper's consultation fee, it's this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.87,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All you young folks ganging up \Nto pick on an old man like me...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're heartless!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not picking on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't go on anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, old goat man.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll chop your wood and draw your water for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the reasonable sort, \Naren't you, my straw-hatted lad?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a deal.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.11,0:10:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That old guy sure did seem \Nto dislike pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.14,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he has some grudge against them?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They say the old man is the only person on the island,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.36,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it's been 20 years since \Nhe washed up here from somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.45,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We've met someone like that before, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are you going, Zoro?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? \NI'm going to go look for something to eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt the old man is going \Nto share anything with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! In that case, get some meat!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask for too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your back into it more!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.64,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you youngsters even \Nchop wood right these days?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so. This cleaning is no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do this over, here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.98,0:11:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, get some grass to \Nthe island goats, and fix the hut!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.62,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so tired... \NDon't just stand there, rub my shoulders!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You might pay me a little mind, \Nwithout me having to tell you everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You people really are so much trouble. \NAfter that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, which way is north, \Nand which way is south?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally made it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys still at it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That old-timer has been pushing \Nwork on us, one job after another.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all worn out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.86,0:12:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship was run down, \Nbut it was definitely a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The old guy is the only one here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the old-timer build a pirate ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We just might be in luck here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In any event, let's go have a look.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You say it's at the top of the mountain?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.55,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there's no need to run, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! \NIt'll take too long to get there starting now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, it was this close, in a straight line?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems creepy somehow, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a ghost ship in the mountains, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin, don't say anything like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits of the dead! Didn't I tell you so?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're fireflies!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He used lumber from the local trees.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he stopped midway through.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The old guy really did this?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like it's here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's not here, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.55,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If my guess is correct, that old man is, \Nin actual fact, a former pirate!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably got shipwrecked,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll bet he's the only one \Nwho made it to this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.19,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, he was building this \Npirate ship to get off the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.57,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but a former pirate disliking pirates
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't make any sense, does it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just simple camouflage,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.33,0:14:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep us from finding the treasure he's hidden.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was shady, right from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that furniture in the old man's hut?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.59,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He had some pretty valuable \Nthings together there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! Very astute!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that fainthearted \Nold man was once a pirate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.64,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he might have been \Na famous pirate long ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all else, there's this ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.23,0:14:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a dense forest ahead, with no paths...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.95,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a steep cliff to the rear.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's going to build a boat to escape on,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,why do it up here in the mountains?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you turn back? \NA danger zone, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.43,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can fear those, \Nand still preserve the Navy's justice?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry. \NBut it won't be possible for them
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to get out of that danger zone so easily, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't have gotten too far away.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Smoker, and Hina, \Nleader of the Black Cage Unit,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,let the Straw Hat pirates slip away from them,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but we will stop them at \Nmy hand, no matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.08,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be of no matter, once they \Nare within your grasp, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.84,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin a search at once! \NGo locate where the Straw Hat pirates are!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– Uh, Captain... \N– Let's go, Corporal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you report that island to the captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.44,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw the island, not recorded \Nanywhere in that area of the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep that from the captain for a little while. \NGot it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.20,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? The Straw Hat pirates \Nare probably on that island.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to let you in on something.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.34,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who put down \NCrocodile in Alabasta was...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.80,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, Captain Smoker, hero of the Navy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.83,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a dumbass.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That turns out to be the \Nofficial statement, nothing more.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, who exactly was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.31,0:16:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Straw Hat pirates, apparently.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we took those guys on,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many lives we had, \Nit wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But, sir...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't believe everything \Nyou hear from the higher-ups.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.65,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to fight them head-on, \Nthey'd wipe us out like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.16,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind them, I need you to give \Nme a hand with something, Corporal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get off this island, right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, that funny old man
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is just going to keep slave-driving us.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm staying here. \N– Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.35,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat! I can't fill up on just this stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.57,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's all gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,– I had to go out looking for that food! \N– For the time being, let's head back to the ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.82,0:17:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chopper, we're going back to the ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.58,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay by the old man's side.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just abandon one of my patients, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.87,0:17:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's gotten better. \NIf you feel sorry for him, there'll be no end to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.47,0:17:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,An end?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.63,0:17:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man's heart didn't \Nstop just because he's timid.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So by "there will be an end," you mean...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it. \NThat old man only has three days left.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure slept well.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.37,0:18:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,– Good morning, old-timer! \N– Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is all this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji is a noted cook, so this is delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The island goats told me where the fruit is,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and some points where the fishing was good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}chan{\i0}, I'm warning you, \NI don't have a penny to pay with.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's fishy here. Way too fishy for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a proverb about this, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.82,0:18:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beware of pirates that suddenly become nice."
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.57,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any poison in this, is there?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.21,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural to be kind to the elderly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want any, I'll eat it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.54,0:19:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'm eating, I'm eating!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-timer, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hey, don't startle him! \N– Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.84,0:19:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you've eaten a Devil Fruit, too, have you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.39,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! It truly has been a long time \Nsince I've had anything this good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.49,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-timer, if there's anything we \Ncan do for you, just ask us, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.19,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't leave behind any regrets.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like this kind of food, \NI'll make it for you, anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You will, huh? Well, thanks. \NWow, this really is good.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terribly yummy. \NThis goes beyond yummy!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, old goat man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,– Don't tell me...! \N– It's happening already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,– Oh, no! \N– Hey, stay with us!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! \NIt was so good, I rushed through eating it,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and got it stuck in my throat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.52,0:20:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, your food got stuck in your throat, did it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.36,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure it was too soon for {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Too soon for what?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.41,0:20:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing at all! \NHe means you're eating too quick, old-timer.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind him, have some of mine, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And mine, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.91,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself to this, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Much obliged, much obliged!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This really is good!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.56,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His appetite is on the same level as Luffy's, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does he really only have three days left to live?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.37,0:21:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the records, \Nthere was a man who fought
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.33,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,against some pirates in that \Narea of the sea 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.63,0:21:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and hasn't been seen since.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.29,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now. \NHe was a guy named Zenny, or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.51,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenny?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The bastard wasn't the only thing that went missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge treasure disappeared with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.35,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposing he made it to that island,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.93,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if he has already kicked the bucket...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure doesn't have a life expectancy, does it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already eaten too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting started.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.49,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awesome, mister!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.57,0:23:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are we going to have \Nto look after the old man?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.95,0:23:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.24,0:23:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he's a pirate, or has treasure, \Nit's none of our business, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.20,0:23:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You should embrace a more inquisitive mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our pursuers from the Navy \Nare already that close!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,– Oh, are you scared? \N– I'm not talking to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.38,0:23:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Tricks? \NThe Designs of Zenny the Moneylender!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.76,0:23:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
